videos.description: Omar Payne cleans up Andrew Nembhard's missed 3-point attempt with an emphatic one-handed slam.

videos.description: Florida's Kerry Blackshear Jr. brings down a rebound and swings his elbows to create space, connecting with St. Joseph's Taylor Funk in the process. Blackshear is assessed a Flagrant-2 foul and ejected.
